Package com.norswap.nanoeth.trees.patricia.memory

Class MemPatriciaBranchNode

java.lang.Object
com.norswap.nanoeth.trees.patricia.memory.MemPatriciaNode
com.norswap.nanoeth.trees.patricia.memory.MemPatriciaBranchNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
PatriciaNode
public final class MemPatriciaBranchNode
extends MemPatriciaNode
A branch node in the in-memory patricia tree. A branch has at least two children who differ in the nibble that follows the key prefix corresponding to this branch node. It can also have some attached value, which can happen when variable-size keys are used and there is a key that is a prefix of some other keys. In that case, it can only have a single child.
